hi i just added my server to moparscape serverstatus page and when i registered it said it has to approve my server or something and if my server isn't online i haft to do it again sometime later and the problem is when i try to log in using my no-ip i get error connecting to server so that means my server is offline?:(

please help me!:(

item.description:

Dont use all that no-ip shit.!

do this. - click start and seach for “run” than you have find you “run” type “cmd” after that.
type “ipconfig” and find you ip, and type than in moparscape server status list.

and just google “watsmyip”
